Release notes for version 0.1 of sltv

This software is still under development and is not tested. 

Still not implemented functionalities:
- Encoding in DV (partially implemented)
- Support for DV source
- Video sources switch during transmission (though the choice before
  transmission is supported)
- Mix different video sources, such as computer slides and webcam video
- Support for dynamic audio and video effects during transmission (though the
  choice before transmission is supported)

Known issues:

There are performance issues when using source V4L2 + ALSA. The video recorded
or transmited is sometimes freezing. This problem hasn't been observed while
using test sources.
